{"tid":1928078,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人究竟點學中文","createTime":"2020-03-16T07:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:06:43.000Z","uid":60644,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"13e22051096afd7ac46dad780f6d1080997367ef","tid":1928078,"uid":60644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"最近打打下字冧到呢個問題<br />\n內地有拼音四聲<br />\n台灣有注音<br />\n香港要每個字死記點寫發音?倉頡速成都要中一電腦堂先教<br />\n就算父母老師都唔會每個字教，唔通真係靠寫生字簿<br />\n我知道粵語都有拼音，但係聽講修大學中文先會學<br />\n有冇巴絲記得細個點學中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，sorry for 低能問題"},{"pid":"b9f798fcb382999afdbf4005c5e59d5d0df104c9","tid":1928078,"uid":321658,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"普通話拼音都係近代產物<br />\n你話古代d人點學中文？"},{"pid":"dee1d0f1b8c332c3212e1bb1357c24570d87f0fd","tid":1928078,"uid":78046,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"中文本身就唔係靠拼音"},{"pid":"b77a9f663424135ad6070e0725cbeefc68af72cd","tid":1928078,"uid":122134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"所以係難學<br />\n我地自己唔識既中文<br />\n咪見邊讀邊 錯都照讀"},{"pid":"c881163470b8ba72b512fb9245869fa2b409e49f","tid":1928078,"uid":53844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"香港人叻"},{"pid":"fd0a8da1041d3d5fdeab7c5a58d02c149612481c","tid":1928078,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9f798fcb382999afdbf4005c5e59d5d0df104c9","tid":1928078,"uid":321658,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"普通話拼音都係近代產物<br />\n你話古代d人點學中文？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:47:46.000Z","msg":"古人一樣有反切拼音, 字典入面都寫晒"},{"pid":"74c75ee595f8ff21c170b864388180ed7ce27ccd","tid":1928078,"uid":234589,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實點解你會問呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 